OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe odd
OL,6,Fshower may continue into this evening,
OL,7,Fbefore turning dry overnight with a
OL,8,Fmix of cloud and clear spells. Light
OL,9,Fwinds. The odd spot of grass frost
OL,10,Fpossible in the countryside.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAnother day with some warm
OL,13,Fsunshine, best of which will be
OL,14,Ftowards the west. Some showers
OL,15,Fpossible in the east come the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Staying mostly dry in many
OL,17,Fwestern areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
