OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FCloudier on Tuesday otherwise staying
OL,7,Fmostly dry and settled during the
OL,8,Ffinal days of April with lots of
OL,9,Fsunshine from Wednesday. Feeling warm,
OL,10,Fbut nights still on the chilly side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
